# --- Dependencies ---
**/node_modules/

# --- Power BI Visuals (pbiviz) Build Junk ---
**/.tmp/
**/.pbiviz/
# Ignore webpack reports but keep the source logic
**/webpack.statistics.dev.html
**/webpack.statistics.prod.html
# Ignore the PBIVIZ certificate files
**/powerbiVisualsCertificate.pfx
**/powerbiVisualsCertificate.cer
**/powerbiVisualsCertificate.pvk

# --- Compiled Output ---
# Ignore everything in the dist folders...
**/dist/*
# ...BUT make an exception so users can download your compiled visual directly.
!**/dist/*.pbiviz

# --- Simulator E2E Data ---
# Ignore the generated CSV test files so they don't bloat your GitHub repo
**/src/tests/output/*.csv

# --- Editor & OS Junk ---
**/.vscode/
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?

# --- Logs ---
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*